# Remember to never publicly share your keystore.
# See https://flutter.dev/to/reference-keystore
#
# Match *anywhere* .jks/.keystore appears in the name, not just as a strict
# suffix — a renamed backup like "my-release-key.jks.WRONG_KEY_BACKUP" doesn't
# end in ".jks" and previously slipped past this gitignore and got committed.
key.properties
**/*keystore*
**/*.jks*
